duck: Sheave - A sheave is a wheel or roller with a groove along its edge for holding a belt, rope or cable.
sheaves definition: a quantity of the stalks and ears of a cereal grass or sometimes other plant material bound together.

milestones: One dead in ski chairlift accident in Switzerland
